<h1>Crepes</h1>

<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Crepes by Chrissy!</p>

<h2>Ingredients</h2>

<ul>
<li>1 c flour</li>
<li>1 c milk</li>
<li>1/2 c water</li>
<li>4 eggs</li>
<li>4 tbsp of butter, melted</li>
<li>3 tbsp sugar</li>
<li>pinch salt</li>
</ul>

<h2>Instructions</h2>

<ul>
<li>wisk all except butter until smooth</li>
<li>let sit for at least 30 min</li>
<li>mix in melted butter</li>
<li>make crepes. ~3 tbsp per crepe</li>
<li>Note: no need to butter the pan.</li>
</ul>
